  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[COUGHS] Some of the important cases, like the military cases on the high command and the southeast, and the hostage case, were tried in a separate large room in the building, which was-- had previously not been used as a court room.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Or if it-- if they had been, it'd been for very minor cases.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was involved in all the industrialist cases and to those parts of the other cases which dealt with economic matters, because I had been appointed to be head of the-- of the Economics Division.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I had used a lot of research analysts to find documents which bore on these-- these cases against Krupp, the Krupp concern, IG Farben, and Flick, and others.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But those are the three that we indicted.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
